---
title: Group Module - User Flow Diagram V2
description: Updated user flow matching Figma screenshots (Team Members, Dashboard, Create Member flows)
date: 07-03-26
version: V2
---

flowchart TD
    Start([User Logs In]) --> Dashboard[Dashboard - Team Overview]
    
    %% Dashboard View
    Dashboard --> ShowMembers[Show Team Members Cards<br/>Alex Morgan, Jamie Chen, Sam Rivera,<br/>Riley Park, Casey Lin]
    ShowMembers --> ShowTaskStats[Show Task Statistics<br/>Total, Pending, Completed per member]
    ShowTaskStats --> ShowLiveActivity[Show Live Activity Feed<br/>Real-time updates]
    
    %% Quick Assign Section
    ShowLiveActivity --> QuickAssign{Quick Assign Section}
    QuickAssign -->|Single Assignment| CreateSingleTask[Create Single Task<br/>Assign to one member]
    QuickAssign -->|Collaborative Task| CreateCollabTask[Create Collaborative Task<br/>Assign to multiple members]
    QuickAssign -->|Personal Task| CreatePersonalTask[Create Personal Task<br/>For yourself]
    
    %% Task Management Section
    Dashboard --> TaskManagement[Task Management Section]
    TaskManagement --> FilterTasks{Filter Tasks}
    FilterTasks -->|All| ShowAllTasks[Show All Tasks]
    FilterTasks -->|Not Started| ShowNotStarted[Show Not Started]
    FilterTasks -->|In Progress| ShowInProgress[Show In Progress]
    FilterTasks -->|Completed| ShowCompleted[Show Completed]
    FilterTasks -->|Personal| ShowPersonal[Show Personal Tasks]
    
    ShowAllTasks --> TaskDetails[View Task Details<br/>Title, Description, Sub-tasks,<br/>Assigned By, Assigned To]
    ShowNotStarted --> TaskDetails
    ShowInProgress --> TaskDetails
    ShowCompleted --> TaskDetails
    ShowPersonal --> TaskDetails
    
    TaskDetails --> TaskAction{Task Action}
    TaskAction -->|Start| StartTask[Start Task<br/>Status: Not Started → In Progress]
    TaskAction -->|Edit| EditTask[Edit Task]
    TaskAction -->|Delete| DeleteTask[Delete Task]
    TaskAction -->|View Subtasks| ViewSubtasks[View Sub-tasks<br/>With progress tracking]
    
    %% Team Members Navigation
    Dashboard --> TeamMembersNav[Team Members Navigation]
    TeamMembersNav --> TeamMembersPage[Team Members Page]
    
    %% Team Members Page
    TeamMembersPage --> ShowTeamStats[Show Team Statistics<br/>Team Size, Total Tasks,<br/>Active Tasks, Completed Tasks]
    ShowTeamStats --> ShowMemberTable[Show Member Table<br/>No, User Name, Email,<br/>Phone, Gender, Role Type,<br/>Tasks Progress, Action]
    
    ShowMemberTable --> MemberAction{Member Action}
    MemberAction -->|View| ViewMember[View Member Details]
    MemberAction -->|Edit| EditMember[Edit Member Profile]
    MemberAction -->|Delete| DeleteMember[Delete Member]
    MemberAction -->|Create Member| CreateMember[Create New Member]
    
    %% Create Member Flow
    CreateMember --> EnterDetails[Enter Member Details<br/>User name, Email,<br/>Phone number, Address]
    EnterDetails --> SelectGender[Select Gender<br/>Male, Female, Other gender]
    SelectGender --> EnterDOB[Enter Date of Birth & Age]
    EnterDOB --> SelectSupportMode[Select Support Mode<br/>Calm, Encouraging, Logical]
    SelectSupportMode --> EnterPassword[Enter Password]
    EnterPassword --> CreateAccount[Create Account]
    CreateAccount --> MemberCreated[Member Created ✅<br/>Added to Team]
    
    %% Permissions Section
    Dashboard --> PermissionsSection[Permissions Section]
    PermissionsSection --> TogglePermissions{Allow Secondary users<br/>to create tasks?}
    TogglePermissions -->|Yes| EnablePermissions[Enable Task Creation<br/>for Secondary Users]
    TogglePermissions -->|No| DisablePermissions[Disable Task Creation<br/>for Secondary Users]
    EnablePermissions --> ManagePermission[Manage Permission<br/>Select which secondary users]
    DisablePermissions --> ManagePermission
    
    ManagePermission --> SelectUsers[Select Secondary Users<br/>Alex Morgn, Sam Rivera, etc.]
    SelectUsers --> SavePermissions[Save Permissions<br/>Changes take effect immediately]
    SavePermissions --> PermissionsSaved[Permissions Saved ✅]
    
    %% Notifications Panel
    Dashboard --> NotificationsPanel[Notifications Panel]
    NotificationsPanel --> ShowNotifications[Show Notifications<br/>Alax tom - Complete math homework]
    ShowNotifications --> ViewAllNotifications[View All Notifications]
    ViewAllNotifications --> NotificationDetails[Notification Details<br/>Task completion updates]
    
    %% Task Monitoring
    Dashboard --> TaskMonitoringNav[Task Monitoring Navigation]
    TaskMonitoringNav --> TaskMonitoringPage[Task Monitoring Page]
    TaskMonitoringPage --> ShowTaskActivity[Show Task Activity Chart<br/>Monthly/Annually view]
    ShowTaskActivity --> ShowTasksByStatus[Show Tasks by Status<br/>Not Started, In Progress,<br/>My Tasks, Completed]
    
    %% Styling
    style Start fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style MemberCreated fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style PermissionsSaved fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style TaskCreated fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style CreateMember fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style ManagePermission fill:#FF9800,color:#fff
